            <div class="h-7 w-2 bg-[#f68c24]"></div>
            <div class="font-bold text-white text-lg w-12 text-left">0:18</div>
            <div class="text-slate-300 text-left text-[17px]">
              Subject seems to be mostly <strong class="font-bold text-white"
